<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الصَّلَاةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> تَجِبُ الخَمْسُ عَلَى كُلِّ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- مُسْلِمٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- مُكَلَّفٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- إِلَّا حَائِضاً وَنُفَسَاءَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَلَا تَصِحُّ مِنْ مَجْنُونٍ، وَلَا صَغِيرٍ غَيْرِ مُمَيِّزٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَعَلَى وَلِيِّهِ أَمْرُهُ بِهَا لِسَبْعٍ، وَضَرْبُهُ عَلَى تَرْكِهَا لِعَشْرٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَحْرُمُ تَأْخِيرُهَا إِلَى وَقْتِ الضَّرُورَةِ إِلَّا:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> مِمَّنْ لَهُ الجَمْعُ بِنِيَّتِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَمُشْتَغِلٍ بِشَرْطٍ لَهَا يَحْصُلُ قَرِيباً.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَجَاحِدُهَا كَافِرٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> الأَذَانُ وَالإِقَامَةُ فَرْضَا كِفَايَةٍ عَلَى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- الرِّجَالِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>